# Input

```yml
a: "double
  quotes" # lala
b: plain
 value  # lala
c  : #lala
  d
? # lala
 - seq1
: # lala
 - #lala
  seq2
e:
 &node # lala
 - x: y
block: > # lala
  abcde

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -5,10 +5,10 @@
 c: #lala
   d
 ? # lala
-  - seq1
+ - seq1
 : # lala
-  - #lala
-    seq2
+ - #lala
+  seq2
 e: &node # lala
   - x: y
 block: > # lala
```

